<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Chicken Note</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="edn100">  100  To &lsquo;fly pigeons&rsquo; was slang for to steal coal. King may stand accused of stealing and receiving. At the same time the charges resemble those made against Earwicker as much as they do throwing stones and making faces. King's language, &lsquo;the vernacular,&rsquo; is the cad's language, decidedly not the King's English.  </div>
